---
title: "shared.ts"

## High-level description
This file defines string constants representing the names of database tables used for managing Carequality directory entries. These constants are used in SQL queries and database operations related to the Carequality directory.

## Code Structure
This file defines three constants that are used as table names in SQL queries. These constants are used by other files that interact with the Carequality directory data.

## References
- `packages/api/src/external/carequality/command/cq-directory/rebuild-cq-directory.ts`
- `packages/api/src/routes/medical/internal-cq.ts`

## Symbols
### `cqDirectoryEntryTemp`
#### Description
A constant string representing the name of the temporary table used to store Carequality directory entries during the rebuild process.

#### Inputs
_None_

#### Outputs
_None_

#### Internal Logic
This constant holds the string value `cq_directory_entry_temp`.

### `cqDirectoryEntry`
#### Description
A constant string representing the name of the main table used to store Carequality directory entries.

#### Inputs
_None_

#### Outputs
_None_

#### Internal Logic
This constant holds the string value `cq_directory_entry`.

### `cqDirectoryEntryBackup`
#### Description
A constant string representing the name of the backup table used to store the previous version of the Carequality directory entries during the rebuild process.

#### Inputs
_None_

#### Outputs
_None_

#### Internal Logic
This constant holds the string value `cq_directory_entry_backup`.
